Lenguaje Herramienta Config JavaScript/TS ESLint <code>.eslintrc.json</code> Python Pylint, Ruff <code>.pylintrc</code> Java Checkstyle <code>checkstyle.xml</code> <p>Setup:</p> <pre><code>// package.json
{
  "scripts": {
    "lint": "eslint src/",
    "format": "prettier --write src/",
    "format:check": "prettier --check src/"
  },
  "husky": {
    "hooks": {
      "pre-commit": "npm run format &amp;&amp; npm run lint"
    }
  }
}
</code></pre>

